This configuration is the automated setup and configuration for all the dot files on linux and mac environments.

For now what is supported is
    - bash
        - ssh completion
        - some bash functions
    - vim
        - vimrc
        - plugins
            - NERDTree
            - bufexplorer
            - git integration
        - syntax
            - markdown
            - textile
            - git
            - python
            - bash
        - colors
